  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/1a01d8530cd2da52.jpg?v=1782535581\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>It has been a little too long since I have shown you any planner related things. To be truthful, <a href=\"http://daydesigner.com/collections/shop-all/products/a5-ring-bound-day-designer-with-starter-insert-pack-white-pebble/#_l_5y/\">my planner</a> these days is not worth showing and there's too much sloppy handwriting and things I would have to blur out anyways. Luckily, I had a good excuse to make a pretty spread in my <a href=\"http://daydesigner.com/collections/shop-all/products/a5-ring-bound-day-designer-with-starter-insert-pack-white-pebble/#_l_5y/\">Day Designer</a> with new <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?B=855179&amp;U=530666&amp;M=65361&amp;urllink=\">Hero Arts</a> planner supplies. I'm part of a blog hop with lots of creatives and three prizes up for grabs to celebrate. October is full on with travel, three big projects I am working on, one of them being something HUGE that I cannot wait to share, and lots of events and trying to stay focused and relaxed. I didn't film the process, but I made sure to take photos. Keeping things simple is the only way to go these days.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/29759577f57cab0c.jpg?v=1782535584\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>I loved using non holiday sets for these two months. No plans for Disneyland, but there were so many other cute ones I had to use. Plus the circles make great indicators of Jack's preschool and I turned the larger circles into pumpkins. I used the washi stamps to indicate travels. </p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"5c-image.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/7d8de46a5a7d851f.jpg?v=1782535587\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"5d-image.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/9ef4ec9a5565cd89.jpg?v=1782535591\">\n